name: Invisible Relationship
tagline: An Invisible Boyfriend and Invisible Girlfriend talk to one another. The world watches. Hilarity ensues.
body:
I read this a few days ago: http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-intersect/wp/2015/01/22/i-paid-25-for-an-invisible-boyfriend-and-i-think-i-might-be-in-love/

I decided it would be fun to make an invisible boyfriend talk to an invisible girlfriend.  So I'm going to make this right now.

Thanks Twilio! Let me know when you want to send me a red jacket!
